{"tid":2192680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［3C老闆］ 被控串媒傷人 保釋被拒 押後至12月7日再訊","createTime":"2020-09-07T09:22:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T10:30:30.000Z","uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8a3f0007515c8dfaddf7b77b7fc48ff4905111fd","tid":2192680,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T09:22:31.000Z","msg":"【3C維修工作室老闆被捕案￼】<br />\n<br />\n3C維修工作室老闆於前日9月5日在其工作的地方被警方上門拘捕，扣留至今日於東區裁判法院提堂，被控串謀有意圖而傷人。被告擔保申請被拒，案件押後至12月7日東區裁判法院再訊，期間需要繼續還押。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/PPPNinternation/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FPPPNinternation%2F&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNpwy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=533ca368\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/PPPNinternation/</a><br />\nIG：<a href=\"https://instagram.com/pppn_international\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fpppn_international&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNpwy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=10b28469\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/pppn_international</a><br />\nTelegram: <a href=\"http://t.me/pppnewstg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fpppnewstg&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNpwy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=7f7a7ddf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/pppnewstg</a><br />\n#PPPN #以曝制暴 #歡迎投稿"},{"pid":"5636cac9aa13489bd10e2cb4dbfc42b6c5d29f34","tid":2192680,"uid":72859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a3f0007515c8dfaddf7b77b7fc48ff4905111fd","tid":2192680,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T09:22:31.000Z","msg":"【3C維修工作室老闆被捕案￼】<br />\n<br />\n3C維修工作室老闆於前日9月5日在其工作的地方被警方上門拘捕，扣留至今日於東區裁判法院提堂，被控串謀有意圖而傷人。被告擔保申請被拒，案件押後至12月7日東區裁判法院再訊，期間需要繼續還押。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/PPPNinternation/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FPPPNinternation%2F&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNpwy7VxIBYRqzliHj24